summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Tenth Avenue North from East Denny Way to North line supple plat of Pinecole Pontius Addition in the City of Seattle, by paving under Ordinance No. 13307, creating Local Improvement District No. 1211 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
